data.description: Welcome to your dream home! This delightful 3 bed, 3 bath oasis is a blend of style & comfort. With an open-concept floor plan, a kitchen sure to ignite your culinary passion, and a primary bedroom that's the perfect haven for relaxation. But the joy of living here extends beyond the indoors! Enjoy lovely outdoor gatherings on the covered patio and never worry about storage or parking with a spacious 2-car garage. Adding to its charm are trim lights with 180 settings to set the perfect ambiance. And the cherry on top, excellent schools and shopping options are just a stone's throw away. Don't miss this rare opportunity to own a home that's been crafted with all the amenities you need for easy and stylish living.
